Amazing app. For a children's app there's a lot of effort put into this. Every animation and interaction is dynamically generated(not hard-coded tween) and there's a game-like element in every character that keeps my kids entertained for hours.  I'm quite impressed with the art, animation and the quality of interaction.  Dynamic orange-chasing ostrich, quilt puzzle, igloo with residents that changes clothes on every opening... Even for a simple guitar object, every string plays a different sound!  Overall very happy with the product.  P.S. There's a tiny glitch at the tip of the 'sock' when stretched.
